</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="878824CAE63B47A06E5895EB5C55B282" pageId="null" pageNumber="518" type="description">
<paragraph id="B77A404BC58A42C5561A04E428E1E814" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="F7E42971A55EF6D8EFA5217D0210EFD7" class="Liliopsida" family="Juncaceae" genus="Luzula" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="518" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="nemorosa">
<emphasis id="B58A3C01F89BAE3C64BE212CD710FC75" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">
<authorityName id="D447C476AAF654929628056C0E573EF2" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">L.</authorityName>
nemorosa
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 6) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="4706284E7618FF8A995D746EA7BFB606" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">
Unterste 
<normalizedToken id="8CBB23DBB9A9ACBB62DDCC58BC66BD33" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="6D3C0F3D444FA3FE7C7C9AD56FF4102D" originalValue="fadenförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">fadenfoermig</normalizedToken>
; 
<normalizedToken id="0421EE7280CFA9F14E8A59048019375E" originalValue="Perigonblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">Perigonblaetter</normalizedToken>
alle gleich lang;
</emphasis>
reife Frucht meist wenig 
<normalizedToken id="0317EA8CE7CF32A9D1E289F7A05F5AA3" originalValue="kürzer" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">kuerzer</normalizedToken>
als die 
<normalizedToken id="1854B47F6BF310A9781A2057B9B44789" originalValue="Perigonblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">Perigonblaetter</normalizedToken>
. - 
<normalizedToken id="910E3C23D34FB0A9B6715DD5F63210A5" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="A32D18449667CED5E734358C3B100BD0" originalValue="Früher" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">Frueher</normalizedToken>
Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="448DF6F6EA35B67124B3987453D11D67" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">
<emphasis id="198E6F720FF389195800F9819B082ECB" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="CFD09942E2A3BF19F516C5235E4F66CE" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">
<emphasis id="2D4DDE78DF8C0E75C51F7E2B94493AC6" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin, montan und subalpin. 
<normalizedToken id="3732993494242AB4AEE8B05EBCC7B76C" originalValue="Wälder" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">Waelder</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="17282EBF712B5B80A4DBEF2DEC7070C5" originalValue="Gebüsche" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">Gebuesche</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D0F384F37FE3BCA6BEF6A55C168160C0" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">
<emphasis id="6D99E0C25BB0161C0E8C9096A07D9C40" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">Verbreitung. Westalpin-apenninische Pflanze:</emphasis>
Seealpen bis Kottische Alpen (Mont Cenis), Korsika, Apennin (
<normalizedToken id="FC6A77091F809EFFE8EF62382CF22EBC" originalValue="südwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="518">suedwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Pistoia bei Florenz, Monte Pisano). - Im Gebiet: Mont Cenis.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
